'From Squeak3.2gamma of 15 January 2002 [latest update: #4881] on 13 June 2002 at 12:55:46 pm'!"Change Set:		selTranslateFix-nkDate:			13 June 2002Author:			Ned KonzThis fixes a problem with selection within translated PasteUpMorphs."!!SelectionMorph methodsFor: 'initialization' stamp: 'nk 6/13/2002 12:52'!extendByHand: aHand	"Assumes selection has just been created and added to some pasteUp or world"	| startPoint handle |	startPoint _ self position.	handle _ NewHandleMorph new followHand: aHand		forEachPointDo: [:newPoint | | localPt |			localPt _ (self transformFrom: self world) globalPointToLocal: newPoint.			self bounds: (startPoint rect: localPt)]		lastPointDo: [:newPoint | selectedItems isEmpty ifTrue: [self delete]												ifFalse: [self doneExtending]].	aHand attachMorph: handle.	handle startStepping.! !